'''Mohammed Waheeb Abu Al-Shamat''' ({{langx|ar|محمد وهيب أبو الشامات}}; born 11 August 2002) is a [[Saudi Arabia]]n [[association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[Defender (association football)#Full-back|right-back]] for [[Al-Qadsiah FC|Al-Qadsiah]] and the [[Saudi Arabia national football team|Saudi Arabia national team]].<ref>{{cite web |title=Mohammed Waheeb|url=https://www.kooora.com/%D9%83%D8%B1%D8%A9-%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%82%D8%AF%D9%85/%D9%84%D8%A7%D8%B9%D8%A8/%D9%85%D8%AD%D9%85%D8%AF-%D9%88%D9%87%D9%8A%D8%A8-%D8%A7%D9%94%D8%A8%D9%88-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%B4%D8%A7%D9%85%D8%A7%D8%AA/ykqvPc8RRh4nOzf7AjW_J}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=محمد أبوالشامات|url=https://www.ksa-team.com/players.php?id=1300}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=محمد أبوالشامات
|url=https://www.365scores.com/ar/football/player/w.-saleh-94676}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Mohammed Abu Al Shamat|url=https://www.spl.com.sa/en/players/84134/mohammed-abu-al-shamat}}</ref>

==Club career==
Abu Al-Shamat started his career at the age of 8 in youth teams of [[Al-Ahli Saudi FC|Al-Ahli]]. He moved to [[Al-Qadsiah FC|Al-Qadsiah]] in 2017. On 5 November 2020, he signed his first professional contract with Al-Qadsiah.<ref>{{cite web |title="القادسية" يوقع 10 عقود احترافية مع "شبابه" |date=5 November 2020 |url=https://akhbaar24.argaam.com/article/detail/518288}}</ref> On 13 August 2024, Abu Al-Shamat renewed his contract with Al-Qadsiah.<ref>{{cite web |title=القادسية يجدد عقد أبوالشامات حتى 2029|url=https://www.al-jazirah.com/2024/20240813/sp8.htm#google_vignette}}</ref>

